data.description: Here is your opportunity to own this beautifully upgraded home in Prestonwood Forest! This spacious 2 story, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with over 3,000+ square feet of living space, has been beautifully upgraded since purchased in 2022 with new upgrades including: New roof, pex plumbing, double pane windows, gutters, french drains, new exterior paint, new shutters, new exterior fence, new water heater, all bathrooms fully remodeled, and refrigerator, microwave, washer, and dryer are also included with the home sale as well!! The first floor features a grand living room with a wood burning fire place, built in shelves, newly maintained carpet, wet bar for entertaining, and a massive game room overlooking the spacious backyard with a covered patio and new fence. All bedrooms are upstairs with ample living space, and fully remodeled full bathrooms. With the elementary school within walking distance and the home conveniently located near HWY 249, this move in ready home is ready for you!
